    "text": "# Upgrading to from version -0.4.0 Some of the interfaces has been upgraded. ## Initialization mermaid_config is no longer used. Instead a call to mermaid initialize is done as in the example below: ### version 0.4.0 ``` mermaid_config = { startOnLoad:true }; ``` ### will look like below in version 0.5.0 ``` mermaid.initialize({ startOnLoad:true }); ```",
